#TBT to last year’s Ferrari Racing Days where more than 100 Ferraris raced around Road Atlanta.⁣
⁣
Tomorrow, #FerrariRacingDays is back, this time at the renowned Indianapolis Motor Speedway. Prepare for an even more spectacular event with just as many Ferraris in attendance, but with the special addition of the iconic Ferrari Monza models.⁣
⁣
Tune in to live.ferrari.com to follow the action.⁣
⁣

node.text: How can a dream come true? Through an immense passion and an enormous commitment. It is through this vision that Enzo Ferrari has built one of the most iconic brands the world has ever seen. A vision that always puts excellence and quality first, infused in all the people that have crossed the threshold of the gates of Maranello, working to preserve its legacy. On this day, 33 years after his passing, we are #RememberingEnzo.
